data.description: ***Wonderful Upgraded Single Story 4 Bedroom Home on a Large Lot that is almost 13,000 sq ft with Solar***From the moment you pull up, you know this house is special. The inviting front yard leads you to the large porch and double-door entry. Upon entry, the grandeur of high-beamed ceilings greets you, enhancing the sense of space in this thoughtfully designed home. Recently painted, the expansive floor plan exudes a fresh, inviting ambiance. The living room stands out with an abundance of natural light and a focal point fireplace that sets the tone for cozy gatherings. Connected to the living space is the dining room, adorned with sliding glass doors that open to the vast backyard. The kitchen, a culinary haven, boasts stainless steel appliances, upgraded fixtures, and an open layout that effortlessly flows into the family room. This family hub has recessed lighting and its own slider to the backyard, offering both comfort and accessibility with direct garage access. Discover tranquility in four generously appointed bedrooms. The primary bedroom is a sanctuary with high ceilings, a walk-in closet, a ceiling fan, and a barn door leading to a lavishly upgraded ensuite bathroom. An additional hall bathroom, also upgraded, caters to the other bedrooms, ensuring every corner of this home reflects luxury. Outside, the big backyard is a canvas for relaxation and entertainment. A custom pergola and patio with a bar create an ideal space for gatherings. Practical touches include a dog run and a shed. The home is equipped with an upgraded HVAC system and an upgraded water heater, ensuring efficiency and comfort in every season. Strategically located in the heart of California City, this home is a gateway to convenience, with easy access to dining, shopping, and other amenities. Experience the epitome of California living in this meticulously upgraded residence that harmonizes luxury with practicality.
